{"type":"answer","id":25893,"parentType":"question","parentId":6238,"uid":4341,"contents":"品韭，就是品尝韭菜人用血汗酿成的酒。<br>\n<br>\n<b>坠好是主席头像同款的。象征所有韭菜人的功劳都是他的。</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NUqjTqe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NUqjTqe.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NUqjTqe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>然后用韭悲盛。自己的血汗被随便洒掉，韭菜们都很悲伤，即“韭悲”。</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmxImL4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmxImL4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kmxImL4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>坠后，干（gàn）了悲韭！</b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vpr2Se3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vpr2Se3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vpr2Se3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-11","agreeCount":22,"discussionCount":0}